nodes.text: Raid on the Golden Nyss Shipyards
Yinchorri raided the Golden Nyss Shipyards in 33 BBY.
The goal was to capture a number of Attack ships and Golden Nyss fighters from the Golden Nyss Shipyards.

Yinchorri troops were smuggled in by Vilmarh Grahrk, who was able to fool the shipyard master, Gzin. Successfully having captured their ships and having blown up the shipyards, the Yinchorri were free to launch their main offensive.
